{"type": "article", "id": 46654, "title": "古力娜扎代言 PUMA，以及，Virgil Abloh 拿下年度最佳球鞋奖 ︳浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-10-30T03:29:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1908, "name": "MacBook"}, {"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 1099, "name": "资生堂"}, {"id": 36433, "name": "J.C Penney"}, {"id": 18584, "name": "Virgil Abloh"}, {"id": 44229, "name": "古力娜扎"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171030111208ce9xSKQ0dARIgY43.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/loreal-halts-shiseido-hire-of-former-executive-11037876/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>欧莱雅禁止前高管加入资生堂申请获批</strong></a> ︳上周，欧莱雅集团针对原美国消费品高级副总裁 Antonios Spiliotopoulos 将加入竞争对手资生堂担任主要职务一事向美国法院提起诉讼。欧莱雅称，Spiliotopoulos 在“个性化”彩妆产品的开发过程中了解了大量机密和专业信息，加入资生堂将对欧莱雅构成竞争威胁。纽约法院通过了该项申请，资生堂目前还未对此事作出回应。</p><p><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2017/10/27/jcpenney-results/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>J.C Penney 或将出现亏损，股价大跌</strong></a> ︳上周五，美国连锁百货 J.C Penney 发布第三季度盈利预警，预计同店销售额将增长 0.6% 至 0.8%，或将出现亏损。消息一出，J.C Penney 的股价大跌 25%，一度低至每股 2.75 美元。</p><p><b>PUMA 宣布古力娜扎为大中华区品牌代言人</b> ︳上周五晚，PUMA 在上海举办了一场拳击训练体验活动，并正式宣布女演员古力娜扎成为大中华区品牌代言人。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030103926cWpMnG2kP69wEDxZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030103926uYmAWfbaPI07k4yw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030103926FnNMldwq7gImUHXf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Apple 推出了一款 12 寸 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/10/apple-macbook-sleeve-leather\" rel=\"nofollow\">MacBook </a>皮套，共有棕色和深蓝两种颜色，售价 149 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301102263P9wILiSBec6g1o7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110225s7UgBomOIlELnfuD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110229ElLtfAsrx5pUGjNZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110229vrYKQWA52lDdIGHa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>继东京、巴黎、首尔之后，LV 品牌历史新展“<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/27/louis-vuitton-volez-voguez-voyagez-exhibition-nyc/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Volez，Voguez，Voyagez</a>”在纽约开幕。<br></p><p>这场展览回顾了 1854 年品牌创立至今超过 160 年的历史。将开放至明年 1 月 7 日，地址为美国证券交易所前址 86 Trinity Place。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110256MRtBgQSsNnHWbi4L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.525000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110301KkeFwoJnzASZVhjR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017103011031374IEhk0YKoayWMwc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110308Bvxg9uoeLEDl2b4Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110259nwCAeyhvVBGxMb8E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110301wumWrTyHOU4SJncE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110305jk4QqgPRMhSHedA6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301103083TXOoyejGw0LW2Yg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301103117zBaJLyXfGucQxnh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110312nHAGzEMtFes84o5g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110314A0YoxpvjOmJSzQXr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110315Lgk9zQXJRhpvH4lA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301103154PpsaBxNJUY2cqHW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110317S7IhnXUtjJZMKVqF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110318Qt0iejdHzk8ngOpD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110318S3OJhd0qapbR1KIo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110321M7s2ienwy3PfWEzd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110345DNiY5BryRLESgUlo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301103460kln8ARtCKbmGgMF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110347AGjE70w8g5x1IuOv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/29/vans-north-face-