in: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110510Se9p3W741lXEh6LQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110510lWEz9D4hfduNTqsP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110510oAxhfuDZGIJnaRY3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301105103tw7U4JIcLFvBlo0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110510ZNnKg8PovMBVEzCF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301105108XbjIK49EVec3F1n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110510ldmAOYCzV3H2FIry.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301105101iqaYRU257HLegZy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110511QOJALhdDK9B7bmEv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301105243St1hQEIZmOC8Ua2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110524o5NUWfeHIyusMGFc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110524hBWFm9D2cgobMtX7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110524W2SxdbBgzrctX1mu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110525EYz9nSPCaNgXsu8y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110525s7rKqB9deY0pD6JP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110525MV1k65ABixhLgqGX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301105259CiLwtmMxKerIuJA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>日本品牌 <a href=\"http://highfashionliving.com/trove-springsummer-2018-lookbook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Trove 的 2018 春夏系列</a>也不错，以大地色为主调，融合了日本传统和服和中东 Sarong Wrap Pants 元素，很清新。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110557qOyExckWl2pt6joX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110549qBpXJEjAu2hSfcH7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110549tsxbqQAMR7kOomj8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110550Vdp7HmOz0iGS4Cjb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110552AlHV2zZB3GkId5eU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110552y0E3df9uN27i5jvt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110552xO5drk6jpHERvK7q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110554PiedL1tXDxh9ZM2r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110554TuXU5Ma1pJyPRnlD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110554z27FqWdnAS3U6RVC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110554pknjvsYRXASe6ZTE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110555CqHpYaMDfyWtGhJk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110555H1TpcOMbCid0qUNz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110556iUHSjLtGb8IhPRJp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110556PjmVfFSYwLkGaodr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110556eS7iF02tmWkzLhpN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110557taSQMfdsh06Iwmlj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110557eDSUG0tHqC9l4ZLj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110557ofEmCgiX2rJ3pA9R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110558MinQc8lrafp9RqZg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>凭借与 Nike 联名企划的 The Ten 中的 Air Jordan 1，OFF-WHITE 的主理人 Virgil Abloh 夺得<a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2017/influencers/power-players/fn-achievement-awards-2017-virgil-abloh-stan-smith-hailey-baldwin-447969/\" rel=\"nofollow\">第 31 届 Achievement Awards 的年度球鞋大奖</a>。 </p><p>另外，Gianvito Rossi、Ronnie Fieg、Birkenstock 分别获得了年度设计师、年度合作者、年度品牌大奖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171030110643lrEVOJLiCoB5HnYy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710301110001QkxpVA4GhbTJl9P.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.642647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2017/influencers/power-players/fn-achievement-awards-2017-virgil-abloh-stan-smith-hailey-baldwin-447969/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FN news</a></p>"}